-   Scoped under .mg-hero (not bare html[data-mode="dark"]) so the dark overrides
-   apply to the hero only and never leak onto the tide app's own tokens. */
+   Scoped under the landing root (not bare html[data-mode="dark"]) so the dark
+   overrides apply to the landing screen only and never leak onto the tide app.
+   Kept as two single-selector rules (not one comma list): a list of descendant-
+   combinator selectors is mis-cascaded by the test's DOM engine, leaking the dark
+   value onto :root and the hero. Two identical single rules match exactly the
